OL,3,CChildren hospitalised after 'flu
OL,4,Coutbreak' at Eisteddfod
OL,6,FMultiple children who were
OL,7,Fhospitalised following a "flu-like
OL,8,Foutbreak" at the Llangollen
OL,9,FInternational Eisteddfod last night (9
OL,10,FWednesday), are due to be discharged
OL,11,Fthis morning.
OL,13,FIn the latest statement from Public
OL,14,FHealth Wales, their Director of Health
OL,15,FProtection Dr Giri Shankar, said: "The
OL,16,Fvisitors to the Llangollen
OL,17,FInternational Eisteddfod who were
OL,18,Fassessed in hospital last night will
OL,19,Fbe discharged this morning."
