OL,4,Coutbreak' at Eisteddfod
OL,6,FHe added: "Tests carried out on these
OL,7,Fchildren have indicated the presence
OL,8,Fof common respiratory viruses,
OL,9,Fincluding flu. They are being treated
OL,10,Fappropriately and are recovering. The
OL,11,Frisk to the public remains low".
OL,13,FAt the time, the Welsh Ambulance
OL,14,FService declared it an "extraordinary
OL,15,Fmedical incident" and the night-time
OL,16,Fconcert was cancelled as a result.
