OL,6,FAn initial statement released by the
OL,7,Ffestival last night said: "Due to an
OL,8,Fextraordinary medical incident -
OL,9,Ftonight's event has been cancelled. We
OL,10,Fwant to thank our own medical teams
OL,11,Fwho are managing the extraordinary
OL,12,Fmedical incident. We are working with
OL,13,Fthe Ambulance services and medical
OL,14,Fteams managing the incident giving
OL,15,Fthem the support necessary.
