OL,6,F"The Llangollen International
OL,7,FEisteddfod intends to run as normal
OL,8,Ffrom 9am tomorrow, but this will be
OL,9,Fbased on the expert medical advice we
OL,10,Freceive. We apologise for any
OL,11,Finconvenience caused."
OL,13,FAnother statement was released by the
OL,14,Ffestival later, which gave more
OL,15,Fdetails and also confirming the site
OL,16,Fwas clear to reopen by 9am today
OL,17,F(Thursday).
