OL,4,Coutbreak' at Eisteddfod
OL,6,FIt said: "Further to the previous
OL,7,Fstatement, we can confirm that
OL,8,Ffollowing the declaration of an
OL,9,Fextraordinary incident by the Welsh
OL,10,FAmbulance Service, following Public
OL,11,FHealth Wales advice - the incident
OL,12,Frelated to a flu-like outbreak and
OL,13,Frelated to multiple people with
OL,14,Fsimilar symptoms. The extraordinary
OL,15,Fincident was called by the Welsh
OL,16,FAmbulance Service due to the number of
OL,17,Fpeople who presented ill at one time.
