OL,6,F"We are pleased to report our site has
OL,7,Fbeen cleared to reopen tomorrow at
OL,8,F9am, as we continue to welcome the
OL,9,Fworld to Wales. We'd like to thank our
OL,10,Fstaff, medical staff and our
OL,11,Fvolunteers for their swift response
OL,12,Fthis evening."
OL,14,FThe festival is due to run until 13
OL,15,FJuly with a range of events and
OL,16,Fconcerts planned across the duration.
